description:
Does sin have you feeling weighed down? Join Pastor Ted Wilson, president of the Seventh-day Adventist Church, as he dives into the topic of sanctification in part 2 of chapter 27 of The Great Controversy by Ellen White. 

Discover how you can find peace in Christ’s righteousness today!

🔗 To learn more about experiencing true revival, read The Great Controversy by Ellen White at https://greatcontroversyproject.org/ and join us next week for more.
